yTime":"2018-06-13T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"相信大家比解難解都係&quot;上解&quot;<br />\n<br />\n依度有殘體答案 大家睇完就明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/35723043.html?qbl=relate_question_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F35723043.html%3Fqbl%3Drelate_question_2&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4a7e7d37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/35723043.html?qbl=relate_question_2</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"進貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"上解是對於政府與事業單位會計來說。就是下級的財政部門將本年度的財政收入交到上一級的財政部門。<br />\n上解型財政是指下級的財政部門的各種支出(人員工資、採購等)都由上一級的財政部門支付，下級的財政部門的收入全部上解，只留少許辦公費等。"},{"pid":"b67a9e9794409f399a06740a494eff7a87895034","tid":700393,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"可能想篤爆地方債"},{"pid":"6eeb5c6f20f377417cc5df3625cefc5b3212c489","tid":700393,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854363771d969d2bdfaacb59103425d05ab9a1f4","tid":700393,"uid":159960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"會唔會好過mpf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"絕對好過"},{"pid":"2679c2f53f6c8dfc9d42867c16c49baf4fcc9cf4","tid":700393,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"點會同聯想到支爆<br />\n完全無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}